
1) Git clone this repository with the --recurse-submodules flag

    git clone --recurse-submodules https://github.com/ealbin/Docker_Cassandra.git

2) Install Docker:

    http://www.docker.com

3) Use bin/cmd.sh as needed

    bash bin/cmd.sh
    


(reference: http://hub.docker.com/_/cassandra )
    
